text:
{
  "prompt": "An electric bicycle with the following configuration: front wheel is 26 inches, rear wheel is 20 inches with a wide 3.0-inch CST Big Boat tire. The bike uses a central mid-drive motor (like Bafang or Tongsheng), connected via a belt drive to a rear internal gear hub (e.g., Shimano Nexus or Enviolo). The frame is a lightweight hardtail style with front and rear suspension. The battery is a large 48V 40Ah pack integrated into the downtube. The rear swingarm is custom-built to accommodate the wide 3.0-inch rear tire. The overall design is sleek, urban, and functional for delivery use, with a slightly sloped top tube for ease of mounting. Components are black and silver with modern minimalist styling. Shown in a realistic 3D render, side view, isolated on white background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution digital rendering of a custom electric bike with a chrome silver frame. The front wheel is 26-inch with a slick on-road tire, and the rear wheel is a smaller 20-inch with a wide CST Big Boat 3-inch tire. The bike features a central mid-drive motor connected to a belt drive system. There is a visible rear suspension system attached to the rear triangle. The battery is integrated into the downtube, and the bike includes front suspension forks. The design is modern and streamlined, suited for urban use.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A side elevation (orthographic side view) of an electric bicycle featuring a larger 26-inch front wheel with a narrow on-road tire and a smaller 20-inch rear wheel with a wide 3-inch CST Big Boat tire. The bicycle includes a visible mid-drive motor, a carbon belt drive system, and a clearly defined rear suspension shock absorber mounted near the rear wheel. The frame is full-suspension style and colored chrome silver. The front fork is a suspension fork, and the rear swingarm geometry supports the small fat tire. The drawing is clean, technical, and accurate in scale, ideal for design illustration purposes.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution side-view image of a step-through electric bicycle with a long wheelbase and a full-suspension system. The frame is chrome silver with no top tube, creating an open step-through design. The battery is fully integrated into the downtube. The front wheel is a 26-inch road tire, and the rear is a 20-inch fat tire (CST Big Boat). The rear swingarm has an extended range of motion with a large rear shock absorber visible. The bike uses a mid-drive motor with a belt drive system, and both wheels have hydraulic disc brakes. The background is neutral gray, and the bike is sharply lit to highlight its engineering details.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution side-view image of an electric bike with a step-through chrome silver frame that has no top tube. The bike has a 26-inch front wheel with an on-road tire and a 20-inch rear wheel fitted with a CST Big Boat 3.0-inch wide fat tire. It features a mid-drive motor, an integrated battery inside the downtube, and a rear suspension system that is clearly articulated and more mechanically realistic, with the rear shock absorber mounted between the chainstay and the seat tube. The belt drive and internal gear hub are clearly visible. Background is clean and neutral for clear focus on bike design.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution side-view rendering of a modern electric step-through bicycle with a silver aluminum frame. The bike has a 26-inch front wheel equipped with a Schwalbe Marathon 2.0 road tire, and a 20-inch rear wheel mounted with a CST Big Boat 3.0 fat tire. It features a mid-drive motor, a belt drive system, an integrated battery within the downtube, and a rear air shock suspension mounted near the seat tube. The frame has no top tube for easy step-through access. The background is neutral and minimalistic to highlight the bike's proportions and design.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
